data.meta_description: 14 likes, 3 comments - ericriglermusic on April 27, 2023: "Eric Rigler’s CELTIC HOLLYWOOD show tomorrow night 4/28/23 CANCELED. The band is very sorry to hear that our venue, the beautiful CASA ROMANTICA in San Clemente had been damaged by a landslide this afternoon. Such bizarre news but our hearts go out to the staff who are dealing with a lot right now. Please direct all ticket refunds to the venue. We’re so sorry. We’ll see you all again in the near future.".
